PresentationColumn.name: # Completed Activities
PresentationColumn.Description: Number of Completed Activities. Valid only for Inbound and Outbound Email.

PresentationColumn.name: # Completed Activities - Calendar Year Ago
PresentationColumn.Description: Number of Completed Activities Calendar Year Ago. Must be used with a Time Attribute.

PresentationColumn.name: # Completed Activities - Fiscal Year Ago
PresentationColumn.Description: Number of Completed Activities Fiscal Year Ago. Must be used with a Fiscal Period Attribute.

PresentationColumn.name: # Completed Activities over SLA
PresentationColumn.Description: Number of Activities completed over SLA

PresentationColumn.name: # Forwarded Activities
PresentationColumn.Description: Number of Activities forwarded. Valid for Inbound Mail and Phone

PresentationColumn.name: # Outstanding Activities - Day Ending
PresentationColumn.Description: Number of Outstanding Activities at the end of every day. Must be used with Day Attribute.

PresentationColumn.name: # Outstanding Activities - Fiscal Month Ending
PresentationColumn.Description: Number of Outstanding Activities at the end of every day. Must be used with Fiscal Month Attributes.

PresentationColumn.name: # Outstanding Activities - Fiscal Quarter Ending
PresentationColumn.Description: Number of Outstanding Activities at the end of every day. Must be used with Fiscal Quarter Attributes.

PresentationColumn.name: # Outstanding Activities - Fiscal Week Ending
PresentationColumn.Description: Number of Outstanding Activities at the end of every day. Must be used with Fiscal Week Attributes.

PresentationColumn.name: # Outstanding Activities - Fiscal Year Ending
PresentationColumn.Description: Number of Outstanding Activities at the end of every day. Must be used with Fiscal Year Attributes.

PresentationColumn.name: # Outstanding Activities over SLA
PresentationColumn.Description: Number of Outstanding Activities which have gone over SLA

PresentationColumn.name: # Received Activities - Calendar Year Ago
PresentationColumn.Description: Number of Received Activities Calendar Year Ago. Must be used with a Time Attribute.

PresentationColumn.name: # Received Activities - Fiscal Year Ago
PresentationColumn.Description: Number of Received Activities Fiscal Year Ago. Must be used with a Fiscal Period Attribute.

PresentationColumn.name: Average SLA
PresentationColumn.Description: Average SLA. Valid for Inbound Email.

PresentationColumn.name: Average Turnaround Days
PresentationColumn.Description: Average Turnaround Days. Valid for Inbound Email.

PresentationColumn.name: Days over SLA
PresentationColumn.Description: Number of Days an activity has gone over SLA

PresentationColumn.name: Turnaround Days
PresentationColumn.Description: Number of working days for completing an activity. Valid for Inbound Email.
